text: Francisco Emmanuel Ortega III is a Filipino politician from La Union, Philippines, and currently the Governor of La Union. He has been elected two terms as a Governor of La Union. He first won election to Governor in 2016 and was re-elected in 2019. ==References== ==External links== *Province of La Union Official Website Category:Living people Category:PDP–Laban politicians Category:1967 births Category:Governors of La Union
